<p>You might be thinking, what will a Web Developer like me do at a company like Aliph…they build headsets?  Simply put - you will be instrumental in shaping the next phase of mobile communications. Aliph is building upon Jawbone to deliver the world’s best personal communications experiences. Aliph has a sustainable intellectual property advantage and a uniquely talented team to lead the company into multi- billion dollar business.  With offices in San Francisco and Sunnyvale, California, the company is privately held and backed by Khosla Ventures and Sequoia Capital.</p>
